scripts.css-min: sass scss/style.scss css/style.css --style compressed | postcss --use autoprefixer -b 'last 2 versions' css/style.css -o css/style.css
scripts.css-min-watch: sass scss/style.scss css/style.css --style compressed --watch | postcss --use autoprefixer -b 'last 2 versions' css/style.css -o css/style.css
